      </style></div><div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center lg:mt-28 mb-12"><div class="flex justify-center md:justify-start"><img src="/car-images/dodge-hero.jpg" alt="Used Dodge auto parts hero image" class="w-full max-w-md rounded-2xl shadow-xl"/></div><div class="flex flex-col justify-center"><h3 class="font-semibold text-xl md:text-2xl mb-3 text-white">Used Dodge Auto Parts for Sale</h3><p class="text-[18px] leading-[30px] text-[#cecece]">Smart. Affordable. Reliable. That’s PartsCentral. Dodge drivers don’t back down from a challenge. Whether it’s about speed, strength, or grit, their vehicles say it all. At PartsCentral, we help you keep that power alive with used Dodge auto parts that perform, last, and save you money.</p></div></div><div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-14"><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Smart. Affordable. Reliable. That’s PartsCentral.</h3><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 text-[#cecece]"><li>OEM used Dodge auto parts inspected for quality</li><li>Built for performance, strength, and reliability</li><li>Nationwide shipping at competitive prices</li><li>Designed to keep Dodge power alive</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Dodge Drivers Know What Power Feels Like</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">You don’t just drive a Dodge to get from A to B. You drive it because it feels different. It sounds better. It responds faster. And when something’s off, you feel it right away. We’re here for Dodge owners who know their ride inside out. Whether you’re working on your daily Durango, your weekend Challenger, or a trusted Ram pickup, we’ve got the used Dodge parts online to keep it pushing hard.</p></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Popular Dodge Parts We Carry</h3><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 text-[#cecece]"><li>Used Dodge engines for sale, including used 4.7 Dodge engines</li><li>Transmissions and transfer cases</li><li>AC compressors, radiators, heater cores</li><li>ABS modules, brake boosters, control modules</li><li>Bumpers, doors, tailgates, fenders</li><li>Starters, alternators, batteries</li><li>Window regulators, motors, switches</li><li>Suspension, axles, control arms</li><li>Lighting, mirrors, sensors, wiring</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Quality You Can Count On</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">Every used Dodge motor for sale at PartsCentral goes through a full inspection before shipping. No shortcuts. No second guesses. Just tested, working parts that show up ready to install. We only sell parts that we’d trust in our own vehicles.</p></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Get a Quick Quote</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">Tell us what Dodge part you need and we’ll send you a fast, free quote. No calls. No hoops. Just the right part at the right price.</p></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Dodge Models We Cover</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">We stock used parts for just about every Dodge model. Even for rare or older Dodge models, we’ll help you track it down.</p><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-1 text-[#cecece]"><li>Dodge Challenger</li><li>Dodge Charger</li><li>Dodge Dart</li><li>Dodge Durango</li><li>Dodge Avenger</li><li>Dodge Caliber</li><li>Dodge Intrepid</li><li>Dodge Neon</li><li>Dodge Journey</li><li>Dodge Magnum</li><li>Dodge Nitro</li><li>Dodge Omni</li><li>Dodge Ram</li><li>Dodge Grand Caravan</li><li>Dodge Viper</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Why Dodge Owners Stick with PartsCentral</h3><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 text-[#cecece]"><li>Rigorous quality inspections</li><li>Nationwide shipping</li><li>Competitive pricing</li><li>Secure checkout and easy returns</li><li>Prompt customer support available 7 days a week</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Built to Run. Ready to Rebuild.</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">You drive a Dodge because it stands out. Keep it that way with high-quality used Dodge auto parts from PartsCentral. Start your free quote today and bring the performance back where it belongs.</p><p class="mt-4 font-bold text-white">Request a free quote today.</p></div></div><div class="w-full mt-20 py-16 sm:py-20 px-4 sm:px-8  bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 text-center rounded-2xl"><h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Find Quality <!-- -->Used Dodge Auto Parts for Sale<!-- --> Parts Today?</h2><p class="text-white/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8 text-sm sm:text-base">Get fast pricing, expert guidance, and nationwide delivery on quality used auto parts for your <!-- -->Used Dodge Auto Parts for Sale<!-- -->.</p><a href="/" class="inline-block  bg-[#00A3FF]  text-white px-7 sm:px-9 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(0,163,255,0.45)] hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(0,163,255,0.7)] transition-all duration-300 hover:opacity-95">Find My Parts</a></div></section><section class="w-full flex flex-col items-center px-6 py-16 bg-[#07142B] text-[#E8F3FF]"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold font-orbitron mb-10 text-center">USED <!-- -->DODGE<!-- --> AUTO PARTS</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto"><ul class="space-y-2 text-lg leading-7 font-jaldi list-disc list-inside text-[#cecece]"><li>Dodge<!-- --> <!-- -->Engine Assembly</li><li>Dodge<!-- --> <!-- -->Transmission</li><li>Dodge<!-- --> <!-- -->ABS Control Module</li><li>Dodge<!-- --> <!-- -->ABS System (Anti-Lock)</li><li>Dodge<!-- --> <!-- -->AC Compressor</li><li>Dodge<!-- --> <!-- -->AC Compressor Clutch</li>